e":"thinking_tokens","estimated_tokens":261,"estimated_tokens_delta":50,"uuid":"6422d8d7-d202-498c-9bac-f7a612d942a9","session_id":"802dcc07-f06a-4920-82f9-0be55de92fb4"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01KLSwAZoCgYm1cn4gS9p7cW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me start by understanding what I need to do:\n\n1. This is task-002 for the Word Garden project\n2. I need to build a terminal UI and entry point on top of the task-001 engine\n3. The focus directive is on minimal code and simplicity\n\nLet me first check the existing codebase to understand what's already there. I should read the SPEC.md to understand the requirements, and then look at the engine files that are already implemented.\n\nKey requirements:\n- `word_garden/ui.py` - pure rendering functions (render, win_screen, loss_screen)\n- `word_garden/main.py` - the main loop with argparse and I/O\n- `word_garden/__main__.py` - entry point\n- `tests/test_ui.py` - tests for the UI\n- `README.md` - documentation\n\nThe focus is on minimal code and simplicity.\n\nLet me start by reading the existing files to understand the contract.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9376,"cache_read_input_tokens":17302,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":9376},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"802dcc07-f06a-4920-82f9-0be55de92fb4","uuid":"04d304d3-f3f2-471e-bda5-695450784f5f","request_id":"req_011CbxgEjXxb9sLPwMd4vPDA"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01KLSwAZoCgYm1cn4gS9p7cW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll help you build the Word Garden UI and entry point. Let me start by examining th